-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------- --
-- ORGANIZATION OF THE LDP4j DISTRIBUTION                                     --
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------- --
-- v${project.version} --

The distribution is organized in the following directories:

 - bin: this directory includes the LDP4j binaries.

 - documentation: this directory includes additional material required for 
  using LDP4j as well as the JavaDoc of the developer API (under the *javadoc* 
  directory).

 - lib: includes the 3rd party dependencies of LDP4j.

 - licenses: includes the licenses of third-party libraries that are included 
 	as part of the LDP4j distribution.
 
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------- --